These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: baking, photography
Job: doctor, musician
1. Job:doctor is in an even position##4
2. Job:musician == Hobby:photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | photography | baking |
| Job     | musician    | doctor   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Beverage: tea, water
Sport: parkour, cycling
1. Sport:parkour is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:water is on the left of Beverage:tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | water | tea        |
| Sport      | parkour  | cycling |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Music-Genre: folk, trance
Nationality: colombian, american
1. Nationality:colombian is in an odd position##4
2. Music-Genre:trance is on the left of Music-Genre:folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | folk |
| Nationality   | colombian | american |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
Beverage: tea, coffee
Food: lime, apple
1. Beverage:coffee is on the right of Beverage:tea##1
2. Food:apple is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | tea      | coffee |
| Food       | lime | apple    |

